Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.46,0:00:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(白衣下的下流K杯女医生——冲田杏梨)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.17,0:00:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗?一定要好好去对待病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.14,0:00:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医院在很多地方还需要发展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.91,0:00:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要好好处理医患关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.32,0:01:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要充分发挥现代化的服务哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.69,0:01:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.63,0:01:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里都能得到充分发展的... \N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.01,0:01:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院长，你还好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.31,0:01:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰有点... ..不太舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.98,0:01:31.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我现在不上学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.75,0:01:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我毕业于一所英国大学的医学院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.36,0:01:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么学院啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.93,0:01:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是针对男性病人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.87,0:01:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用女人的东西来治疗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.78,0:01:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.98,0:01:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的，院长就来试试吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.12,0:02:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院长可以试吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.25,0:02:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.09,0:02:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院长是不是腰不好么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.39,0:02:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来试试看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.20,0:02:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?.. .可以吗... .0K的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.18,0:02:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.31,0:02:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是女人要先开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.32,0:02:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就先来看看这圆圆的————
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.60,0:02:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.94,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.49,0:03:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔软的曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.79,0:03:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么圆润
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.27,0:03:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.67,0:03:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个圆圆的胸——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.82,0:03:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酥软——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也很有感觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.35,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.12,0:04:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个都感受一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.83,0:04:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不同呢...是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.33,0:04:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会更好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.71,0:04:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有高低差感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.19,0:04:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么的摸着女人的感觉——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.80,0:05:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院长，腰有好点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.07,0:05:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.85,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了...谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.98,0:05:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来女 人的曲线能治疗男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.69,0:05:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了日本医疗技术的发展，就专心好好做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.44,0:05:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.84,0:05:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后为了病人我会好好治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.06,0:06:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.63,0:06:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在说不出口——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.25,0:07:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.22,0:07:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么了，怎么都好不了——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.63,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说啊..就说都没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.30,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生，有点可怜，想想办法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.70,0:07:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不知道原因啊，放弃吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.74,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么放弃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.68,0:07:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，用我的方法试试吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.95,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个吗?也许不行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.62,0:07:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.03,0:07:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油了，保重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.80,0:07:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.17,0:07:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.61,0:08:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，交给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.38,0:08:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会马上就好起来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.09,0:08:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.39,0:08:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松，好好看着我就行了——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.35,0:08:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了提高治疗能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.12,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要先看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是医生身上圆圆的东西哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.17,0:09:03.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是医生身体这个曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.88,0:09:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.08,0:09:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲线哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.23,0:09:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.53,0:09:37.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是要爽起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.81,0:09:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要看好哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.21,0:09:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.02,0:09:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.12,0:09:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圆圆的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.46,0:10:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.97,0:10:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.51,0:10:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了...\N圆哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.79,0:10:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个东西，知道吗 ——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.93,0:10:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个软度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.78,0:10:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.25,0:11:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么柔软圆润，要多多感觉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.00,0:11:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以摸——摸吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.50,0:11:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.59,0:11:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么摇起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.10,0:11:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是给你的特殊治疗，就专心享受吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.76,0:12:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还想要继续吗？\N等一下哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.28,0:12:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着这——动作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.40,0:12:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好圆啊\N是的，要像这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.47,0:13:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用医生圆圆的美胸来按摩就会好起来的——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.65,0:13:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的? ——就是这么用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.80,0:13:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再多一点吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.64,0:13:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话就来用一下吧，为了治你的病情哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.35,0:13:46.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股好圆好酥软——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.15,0:14:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有这种治疗——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最新的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.39,0:14:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就让我来吧\N要快点好起来喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拖了——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.04,0:14:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要充分发挥作用的话就得把衣服脱咯——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.52,0:14:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.50,0:15:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受医生胸部的那份柔软哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.68,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用进去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.19,0:15:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点好了——就是这么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.16,0:15:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再加强点效果吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.37,0:15:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看追软柔摇动的奶吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.81,0:15:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.46,0:16:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又圆又软呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.77,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉越来越有效果哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.66,0:16:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴也来吧——为了康复起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.94,0:16:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃——\N是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.61,0:17:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.75,0:17:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都硬了哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.69,0:17:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬奶头会更有效哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.70,0:17:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.64,0:18:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躺下吧，这是治疗——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.29,0:18:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要给你看好地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.50,0:18:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地兴奋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.89,0:18:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.33,0:18:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顶到软处了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.74,0:19:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看得到兴奋处吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.08,0:19:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦\N那好好盯着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好用到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.96,0:19:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好地硬起来哦——再来一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.60,0:19:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转过去——治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.94,0:19:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.30,0:20:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈来愈好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.80,0:20:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,含了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.83,0:20:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超爽，一起爽，——会更好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.61,0:20:48.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗? 》》》好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.40,0:21:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有效呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更兴奋会更好的——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.43,0:22:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?热东西插入咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.85,0:22:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.63,0:22:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热好软，.这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.78,0:23:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好着着摇动的奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.65,0:23:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.04,0:23:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.44,0:23:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会有效果的——.动得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.05,0:23:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以多用吗?\N再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.63,0:23:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.07,0:24:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好摇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.51,0:24:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.80,0:24:33.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.32,0:24:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让女人湿润起来会更快好的\N这样会更有疗效的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.16,0:25:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加有效的的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.72,0:25:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好用，只是对你的治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.79,0:25:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.84,0:25:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿润了嘛——\N是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:49.61,0:25:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样对身体会有好处的——真的\N所以要多多享用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.00,0:26:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力量插——这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:39.53,0:26:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.40,0:27:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.50,0:27:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多动动才好——是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:29.08,0:27:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好地动吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:52.20,0:27:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了..\N那就好好爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:02.84,0:28:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:20.83,0:28:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都射了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:45.42,0:28:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈像变好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.86,0:28:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?..脏东西这么浓厚呢——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:03.41,0:29:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治好了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:07.81,0:29:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉舒服多了\N.真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:15.52,0:29:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:22.12,0:29:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:36.07,0:29:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,院长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:38.27,0:29:40.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你治疗法真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.04,0:29:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了,来我们医院的病人增加啦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:53.32,0:29:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?\N收益也提高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.09,0:30:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:00.66,0:30:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子可以多赚。。。。不，提升日本的医疗水平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.64,0:30:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的...加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.01,0:30:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.32,0:30:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近手有看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.62,0:30:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又突然不舒服了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.56,0:30:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛得受不了.——等等哦——我叫奥田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.33,0:30:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是奥田先生吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:41.04,0:30:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,, 不好意思，今天下午确诊都满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.28,0:30:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都满了吗? \N就没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.78,0:30:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都痛得受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:57.92,0:31:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有办法减轻一些吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.83,0:31:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以做些治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.17,0:31:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.84,0:31:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实，我可是英国大学毕业的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:26.55,0:31:30.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道最新的治疗法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.32,0:31:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.36,0:31:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会马上好的...真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.03,0:31:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话来试试吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.80,0:31:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比什么都不做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.10,0:31:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛的是这里吗?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.44,0:31:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那失礼了，这么可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.68,0:32:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先维持好.. .好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:05.09,0:32:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是圆的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.76,0:32:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里，很圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.53,0:32:20.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.97,0:32:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.88,0:32:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.39,0:32:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这曲线和圆圆的胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:45.09,0:32:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:51.70,0:32:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里头啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.57,0:33:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要脱哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:02.34,0:33:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做什么?...要先用出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:08.95,0:33:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什委?.. .这个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:11.52,0:33:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么这个啊...就是圆曲软的东东
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.90,0:33:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像这么用——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.50,0:33:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此爽的话——就像这么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:39.41,0:33:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太痛 了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.72,0:33:49.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样的，这很重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.16,0:33:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:55.20,0:33:58.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉软软的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:58.50,0:34:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉了...是吗?..好软啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:02.17,0:34:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样子...不痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:08.04,0:34:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?...其..实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.28,0:34:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是这样还有点没太够，失礼了——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.56,0:34:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么?.. .就是治疗前的准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:32.63,0:34:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是治疗，别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.34,0:34:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要脱啊?...是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:49.15,0:34:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈好看着曲线哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:57.96,0:35:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起爽 才会好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:03.83,0:35:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.44,0:35:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好伸长.这么才会好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.49,0:35:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有看到线条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:31.73,0:35:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了爽就要用痛的手来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:37.23,0:35:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么感觉软的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:42.37,0:35:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好...受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:46.78,0:35:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.55,0:35:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变硬了，对，就这样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.09,0:36:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好揉起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:08.06,0:36:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好圆好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.47,0:36:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很弹是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:19.81,0:36:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是治疗哦，会马上好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.45,0:36:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:40.00,0:36:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多感觉一点..可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.50,0:36:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有人来的话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:49.54,0:36:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关傈，对大家都好的，一起治瘭0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.18,0:37:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感贵很好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.32,0:37:11.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么.很好的身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:13.40,0:37:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要天使湿了的才会好，就像这样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:23.30,0:37:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒躲开了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.25,0:37:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于够到了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:47.53,0:37:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要含进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:11.02,0:38:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好让肉棒热起来会对身体好的——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.73,0:38:21.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好的感觉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:21.66,0:38:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的?那就再多用点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.61,0:38:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来用圆的东西刺激
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:42.95,0:38:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么好好感觉，可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:52.49,0:38:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手夹哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:12.31,0:39:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:18.55,0:39:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感受医生的这份柔软——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.22,0:39:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽...是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:24.43,0:39:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得放松了。.是吗?很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:33.23,0:39:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多用点哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:39.84,0:39:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.65,0:39:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都交给我...真好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.26,0:40:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有爽吗?...已经一片白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:02.23,0:40:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来很有感觉.那就好好感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.08,0:40:23.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快不行了.. .那就好好地爽趋来——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:41.14,0:40:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看不太到，但知道很热了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.13,0:41:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么用会更爽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:16.37,0:41:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么会爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:25.18,0:41:32.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有感觉.. .那就解放吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.15,0:41:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就完全释放了.. .爽起来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.19,0:41:37.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:42.80,0:41:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:49.04,0:41:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.58,0:42:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多啊，等等哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:12.53,0:42:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦呢——这是什么东西呀——\N我尝尝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.41,0:42:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能动了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.71,0:42:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的动了，好棒——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.06,0:42:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒...真的.不痛了呢——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.56,0:42:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢... 很有精神，一 定好了.\N谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:51.07,0:42:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了...还有不舒服的地方就来找我吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.67,0:43:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思，谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.42,0:43:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得那个费用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:16.39,0:43:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:28.87,0:43:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.07,0:43:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好...果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:36.58,0:43:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好转呢.. .多亏你们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.65,0:43:49.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要记得好好吃药哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:51.26,0:43:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:57.87,0:43:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多保重——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.74,0:44:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋品先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:08.51,0:44:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体感觉如何——要量了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:19.15,0:44:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温度有点高了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:25.76,0:44:29.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不好啊. .是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.73,0:44:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想快.点好起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:38.97,0:44:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好处理不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.45,0:44:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:59.53,0:45:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在用最新的治疗方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:06.50,0:45:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心有什么问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:15.31,0:45:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兴趣吗?.. .嗯...是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:28.52,0:45:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有些紧张，倡一定要放松
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:35.50,0:45:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来了哦..拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.66,0:46:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很重要的，要安静，. 知,道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:12.20,0:46:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的就是曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:24.68,0:46:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是曲线和圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:38.26,0:46:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来试一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:47.07,0:46:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:50.74,0:46:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好圆...是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:56.61,0:46:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了 吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:07.62,0:47:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真积极
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:19.00,0:47:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆和曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:37.72,0:47:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有软都是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:54.60,0:48:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要有感觉的就是是这软度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:05.61,0:48:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好谗...还好弹力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:12.59,0:48:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:21.40,0:48:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:25.43,0:48:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对.曲线.圆和软度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:42.32,0:48:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?兴奋了 吧!?...好议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:55.90,0:49:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得软吗?..超软的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:05.07,0:49:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就特别来用吧..可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:13.15,0:49:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:13.52,0:49:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好用开哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:28.56,0:49:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:32.60,0:49:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从后面来用圆和软
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:56.83,0:50:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?有兴奋了吗?..\N好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:06.37,0:50:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:16.28,0:50:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受那三样哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:54.82,0:50:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.42,0:51:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以好好品尝哦.. .可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:39.96,0:51:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:11.53,0:52:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真积极——好痛...对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:17.77,0:52:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受圆哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:27.68,0:52:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:55.94,0:53:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋田先生都这么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:04.75,0:53:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子了.. .有叉应了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:08.78,0:53:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:25.30,0:53:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是治疗哦，要好好用哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:38.15,0:53:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋出先生的老二变好糟糕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:45.12,0:53:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋了啊... 这不太好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:54.30,0:53:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要好好治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:10.81,0:54:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:14.48,0:54:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:20.36,0:54:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来是弄湿的治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:42.57,0:55:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流出来了——\N对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:48.81,0:55:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的身体一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:34.32,0:56:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都这样，可以的话再来特别的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:43.87,0:56:49.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以再来用我的曲线吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:55.61,0:57:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是护士用的，敬请用吧——\N我用？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:04.05,0:57:06.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕开啊..可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:13.96,0:57:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:30.85,0:57:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大胆——
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:38.19,0:57:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把最后一层拨开吧——\N看看里面的小穴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:51.77,0:57:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了...是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:56.17,0:58:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受那里头的东西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:08.65,0:58:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:13.05,0:58:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好湿啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:22.23,0:58:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么湿润啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:32.51,0:58:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋对治疗好，所以——要好好兴奋哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:56.85,0:59:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更湿了...是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:02.73,0:59:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:13.00,0:59:18.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想你好好地用我的小穴——\N这里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:21.45,0:59:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是单纯的玩，哦是要兴奋——\N这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:51.18,0:59:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里头也请吧\N里头?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:56.68,1:00:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来试里头如何\N好热啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:24.21,1:00:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞的治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:59.08,1:01:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交得好起来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:04.58,1:01:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兴奋了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:13.39,1:01:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以来用我的曲线吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:26.60,1:01:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:47.16,1:01:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉吗?\N治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:55.97,1:01:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:15.42,1:02:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流东西出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:11.58,1:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好爽才能治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:35.43,1:03:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:53.42,1:03:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好用哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:35.26,1:04:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉到治疗的效果吗?有爽吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:46.27,1:04:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多爽一点，这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:50.68,1:04:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成为最好的治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:10.50,1:05:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:34.72,1:05:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再兴奋点——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:33.44,1:06:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞——.好兴奋哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:49.23,1:06:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:05.74,1:07:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，再来哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:31.44,1:07:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个都进了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:40.98,1:07:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:02.63,1:08:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:18.42,1:08:22.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要不行了..是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:42.27,1:08:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:35.49,1:09:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:14.03,1:10:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么甜的——就很快就好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:23.21,1:10:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治疗很成功哦，..谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:11.66,1:11:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿这个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:17.90,1:11:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思.虽然是男子更衣室
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:23.03,1:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是女更衣室太多人了.\N可以来这边用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:28.54,1:11:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要换了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:36.25,1:11:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下就好别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:41.02,1:11:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里换就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:48.73,1:11:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，你是505房的平井先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:56.43,1:12:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊——\N还没出院?...是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:03.78,1:12:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:12.22,1:12:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我换衣服了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:26.53,1:12:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:40.48,1:12:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里啊为什么有女人用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:57.73,1:13:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井先生——身体还有些地方不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:08.37,1:13:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真担心你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:13.88,1:13:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我知道最近的治疗法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:23.05,1:13:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最新的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:27.83,1:13:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以让我试吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:34.07,1:13:37.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子?...对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:39.20,1:13:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然最新但很简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:49.48,1:13:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:57.19,1:14:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起.都遮住了.要让你看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:07.83,1:14:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:12.60,1:14:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲线还有圆哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:22.51,1:14:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:29.12,1:14:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好圆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:37.56,1:14:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这个圆——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:47.84,1:14:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清楚此较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:05.46,1:15:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快..点好才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:08.39,1:15:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有人来的...那么就快用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:16.83,1:15:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会好的哦，看到了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:24.54,1:15:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:32.25,1:15:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是这软
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:45.46,1:15:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这大圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:51.70,1:15:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接这么来的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:01.98,1:16:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗?是这么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:11.52,1:16:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看这哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:17.40,1:16:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样会好吗?..当然.很有效的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:32.08,1:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲线才是女人最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:15.39,1:17:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是很圆的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:34.47,1:17:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:39.98,1:17:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是男衣室啊..是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:47.69,1:17:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女人，才要这么下流啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:56.13,1:17:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对..是为了治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:00.53,1:18:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是治疗哦，好好看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:19.25,1:18:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平井先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:27.33,1:18:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住院会不安的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:36.87,1:18:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是护士，会好好用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:47.15,1:18:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:55.22,1:18:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾好好用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:59.99,1:19:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好意思...怎么?为了治疗都要
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:10.64,1:19:15.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是要好好用的...不应该吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:16.51,1:19:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:25.32,1:19:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这圆要怎么用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:33.76,1:19:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这么来按摩的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:19:49.17,1:19:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有治疗的感觉了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:08.99,1:20:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是圆和软
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:18.54,1:20:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圆和软哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:25.51,1:20:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是治疗哦）多加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:39.46,1:20:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好软...有感觉到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:51.94,1:20:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这瑟来刺激哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:20:57.44,1:21:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然要全用上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:24.24,1:21:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:33.04,1:21:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来才是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:37.45,1:21:44.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是最新治疗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:45.16,1:21:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为好好用.就要对这些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:21:56.53,1:21:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么来用可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:02.77,1:22:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是最新的药哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:19.29,1:22:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那来咯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:35.44,1:22:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不行.再多用..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:42.05,1:22:47.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体也直接用上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:22:52.32,1:23:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆的地方也要好好用上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:10.31,1:23:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用好了，可以了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:22.05,1:23:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来用咯——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:44.44,1:23:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好滑...有感觉了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:50.31,1:23:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:23:55.82,1:23:57.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:00.59,1:24:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:05.00,1:24:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:23.35,1:24:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:29.22,1:24:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:37.66,1:24:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:44.27,1:24:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面都起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:47.94,1:24:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了治疗让我来用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:53.81,1:24:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:56.75,1:25:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来是最后一阶段了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:09.23,1:25:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湿了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:21.71,1:25:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?有感觉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:38.22,1:25:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用上药有更兴奋吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:49.60,1:25:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋就来更爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:25:56.57,1:25:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对治疗好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:20.80,1:26:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软吗?那太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:27.04,1:26:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感觉才会好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:26:50.90,1:26:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:22.83,1:27:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗?有治疗了吗?——\N好好感受哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:27:55.49,1:28:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了...是吗?\N射出来吧，这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:17.88,1:28:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要射了...全射出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:41.74,1:28:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都射出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:28:52.38,1:28:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一定会治好的....真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:01.93,1:29:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么有精神就一定会不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:23.95,1:29:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野谷先生还不想睡吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:29.82,1:29:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:34.23,1:29:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是睡不着...每天?但是都这时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:41.20,1:29:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊...怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:45.24,1:29:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道呢，就是这样——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:52.21,1:29:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:55.51,1:29:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得一直这么呢，是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:00.28,1:30:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过也没影响它人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:05.79,1:30:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为了你来用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:14.23,1:30:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就用紧急才用的治疗法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:26.34,1:30:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那个?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:30.38,1:30:34.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊...那麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:35.52,1:30:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要先看要点——可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:57.91,1:31:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了说明哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:11.12,1:31:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一个是曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:21.77,1:31:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是女人的曲线
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:32.78,1:31:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:38.28,1:31:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:50.40,1:31:54.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓到，这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:54.43,1:31:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:57.37,1:32:00.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个就是圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:00.30,1:32:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:06.18,1:32:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圆是很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:11.32,1:32:12.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好比..
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:16.45,1:32:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屁股也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:20.86,1:32:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?...真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:26.00,1:32:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能快点好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:32.60,1:32:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:42.51,1:32:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是软
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:50.59,1:32:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看好哦.. .好弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:32:58.30,1:33:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹和软都能爽的...太赞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:10.78,1:33:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗?...很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:19.58,1:33:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看曲线吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:29.86,1:33:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:39.77,1:33:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:33:49.31,1:33:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗?...这是为了病人哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:02.53,1:34:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美的东西.. .是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:14.64,1:34:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,病人得快点好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:23.08,1:34:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要让你看圆了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:38.50,1:34:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?...当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:42.90,1:34:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:50.61,1:34:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:53.91,1:34:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感受圆
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:34:59.42,1:35:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好软好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:07.49,1:35:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前头要硬哦...最近都没感受到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:15.20,1:35:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那很不好哦.好好感受
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:30.25,1:35:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这好赞...这么能用才是最赞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:47.87,1:35:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来双手用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:35:57.04,1:35:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:06.22,1:36:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不知，但要爽哦...好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:20.90,1:36:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽就好好用
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:25.67,1:36:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:33.38,1:36:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面来用哦.\N可以吗?.. 来用吧——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:45.86,1:36:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:36:52.10,1:36:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:09.35,1:37:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以用开吗?要多看圆哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:15.95,1:37:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好用哦.. .不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:24.03,1:37:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:37:49.72,1:37:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了吗?...好赞——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:01.83,1:38:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣哦，湿热要好好用哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:10.64,1:38:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好赞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:20.18,1:38:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些兴奋了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:26.06,1:38:27.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来用更多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:30.09,1:38:31.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:20.75,1:39:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好，多用点——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:30.66,1:39:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真好——有感觉了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:39.83,1:39:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好感受哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:39:47.54,1:39:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松才有效，舔奶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:04.42,1:40:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放松了吗?.\N嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:08.46,1:40:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸出声音来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:32.34,1:42:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来要好好含了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:41.51,1:42:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是治瘰哦——别担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:53.99,1:42:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:43:48.31,1:43:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更硬了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:11.44,1:44:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有感觉吗?我们继续了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:44:55.48,1:44:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:12.36,1:45:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:16.40,1:45:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都看得那么多了，那就来继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:28.15,1:45:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:36.41,1:46:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那个勃起起来的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:42.29,1:46:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就来插我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:52.93,1:46:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK吗?要上咯——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:13.48,1:47:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热...是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:36.97,1:47:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽...真的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:40.65,1:47:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是治疗吗?.. .这是治疗哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:48.72,1:47:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超爽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:10.37,1:48:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了自己的不适吧. .就忘了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:23.22,1:48:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何?.. .好爽.什么都不知道了|
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:27.63,1:48:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有爽吗?...好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:37.54,1:48:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好好用吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:01.76,1:49:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:14.24,1:49:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人兴奋的话.就可以很快好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:47.64,1:49:51.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:59.02,1:50:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的角度哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:03.79,1:50:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:26.18,1:50:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小穴觉得好像有东西通过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:47.10,1:50:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好好爽吧——已经够爽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:58.48,1:51:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么深吗?.. .\N看好然后再——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:54.27,1:51:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好用着吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:01.24,1:52:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好滋润啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:25.10,1:52:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:33.54,1:52:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:52:53.72,1:52:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要舔穴吗?...当然
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:01.26,1:54:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽——\N我也是——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:06.03,1:54:08.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好摸着好好爽——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:10.44,1:54:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么用的吗?...这些很重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:22.91,1:54:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好治好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:26.58,1:54:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽得要受不了了..\N可以的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:32.09,1:54:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以就把肉棒里的东西射到我舌头上
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:54:54.11,1:54:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:13.20,1:55:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以射出来吗吗?...\N这是治疗哦，射出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:05.68,1:56:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超黏的精子\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:12.29,1:56:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以睡了呢——\N那就好好用了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:23.67,1:56:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好睡觉哦——
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:49.36,1:56:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来没事，我刚才已经听诊过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:56:55.60,1:57:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药要记得都要吃哦\N这样的话才会康复的更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:05.14,1:57:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦了..谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:13.22,1:57:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那治疗法，一年后我成了医院的大咖
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:22.39,1:57:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在后来我成了医生\N虽然周围也有一些其他的评价——
